UBS’s Middle East Equities Head, Rikin Patel, Said to Leave

-- B y   Z a h r a   H a n k i r   a n d   S t e f a n i a   B i a n c h i
-- 
2011-06-19T12:48:40Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-19/ubs-s-middle-east-equities-head-rikin-patel-said-to-leave.html
Rikin Patel,  UBS AG (UBSN) ’s head of
equities in the  Middle East  and North Africa, left the Swiss
bank, two people with knowledge of the matter said.  Patel joined UBS in 2005 from JPMorgan Chase & Co. and
became the MENA equities head in 2008, according to Bloomberg
data.  Patel couldn’t be reached for comment. Officials at UBS in
 London  declined to comment.  To contact the reporters on this story:
Zahra Hankir in Dubai at 
